#. <section class="sutta" id="sn12.3"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn12.3:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 12"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 12"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.3:0.2"
msgid "1. Buddhavagga"
msgstr "1. The Buddhas"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn12.3:0.3"
msgid "3. Paṭipadāsutta"
msgstr "3. Practice"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.3:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati … pe …"
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn12.3:1.2"
msgid "“micchāpaṭipadañca vo, bhikkhave, desessāmi sammāpaṭipadañca."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I will teach you the wrong practice and the right practice."

msgctxt "sn12.3:1.3"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha, sādhukaṃ manasi karotha, bhāsissāmī”ti."
msgstr "Listen and pay close attention, I will speak.”"

msgctxt "sn12.3:1.4"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”ti kho te bhikkhū bhagavato paccassosuṃ."
msgstr "“Yes, sir,” they replied."

msgctxt "sn12.3:1.5"
msgid "Bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr "The Buddha said this:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.3:2.1"
msgid "“Katamā ca, bhikkhave, micchāpaṭipadā?"
msgstr "“And what’s the wrong practice?"

msgctxt "sn12.3:2.2"
msgid "Avijjāpaccayā, bhikkhave, saṅkhārā;"
msgstr "Ignorance is a condition for choices."

msgctxt "sn12.3:2.3"
msgid "saṅkhārapaccayā viññāṇaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "Choices are a condition for consciousness. …"

msgctxt "sn12.3:2.4"
msgid "evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa samudayo hoti."
msgstr "That is how this entire mass of suffering originates."

msgctxt "sn12.3:2.5"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, micchāpaṭipadā."
msgstr "This is called the wrong practice."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.5"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.3:3.1"
msgid "Katamā ca, bhikkhave, sammāpaṭipadā?"
msgstr "And what’s the right practice?"

msgctxt "sn12.3:3.2"
msgid "Avijjāya tveva asesavirāganirodhā saṅkhāranirodho;"
msgstr ""
"When ignorance fades away and ceases with nothing left over, choices cease."

msgctxt "sn12.3:3.3"
msgid "saṅkhāranirodhā viññāṇanirodho … pe …"
msgstr "When choices cease, consciousness ceases. …"

msgctxt "sn12.3:3.4"
msgid "evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa nirodho hoti."
msgstr "That is how this entire mass of suffering ceases."

msgctxt "sn12.3:3.5"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, sammāpaṭipadā”ti."
msgstr "This is called the right practice.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn12.3:3.6"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
